WEBVTT

00:15:58.579 --> 00:16:00.489
who made house calls,

00:16:00.489 --> 00:16:03.380
who was a public servant.

00:16:03.380 --> 00:16:05.203
These aren't such new ideas

00:16:05.203 --> 00:16:07.565
of what medicine should be.

00:16:07.565 --> 00:16:10.290
What's new is the scaling up

00:16:10.290 --> 00:16:13.673
and the faces of the doctors themselves:

00:16:13.673 --> 00:16:17.130
an ELAM graduate is more likely to be a she

00:16:17.130 --> 00:16:19.060
than a he;

00:16:19.060 --> 00:16:21.987
In the Amazon, Peru or Guatemala,

00:16:21.987 --> 00:16:24.338
an indigenous doctor;

00:16:24.338 --> 00:16:27.352
in the USA, a doctor of color

00:16:27.352 --> 00:16:29.748
who speaks fluent Spanish.

00:16:29.748 --> 00:16:33.427
She is well trained, can be counted on,